OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1774563066
OL,3,CDualling of A66 between Penrith (M6)
OL,4,Cand Scotch Corner set to begin this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FWork to fully turn the A66 between
OL,8,FPenrith and Scotch Corner into a dual
OL,9,Fcarriageway will commence this year
OL,10,Funder government plans.
OL,12,FThe complete dualling of the road
OL,13,Fwhich connects the M6 to the A1(M) is
OL,14,Fpart of a #2billion programme of road
OL,15,Fworks for the North East and Yorkshire
OL,16,Fannounced today.
OL,18,FThe plans were initially approved in
OL,19,F2024 under the Conservative
OL,20,Fgovernment, but these were put under
OL,21,Freview when Labour came into power.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1774563066
OL,3,CDualling of A66 between Penrith (M6)
OL,4,Cand Scotch Corner set to begin this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe Department of Transport has now
OL,8,Fconfirmed work will begin in 2026,
OL,9,Fwith further details expected to be
OL,10,Fpublished later this year.
OL,12,FThe department said: "The A66 is one
OL,13,Fof the largest and most important road
OL,14,Finvestments in the North of England.
OL,16,F"The route plays an essential role in
OL,17,Fconnecting people and places across
OL,18,Fthe north of England, and for journeys
OL,19,Fbetween Scotland and the eastern side
OL,20,Fof England; it is critical for freight
OL,21,Fand links to international ports.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1774563066
OL,3,CDualling of A66 between Penrith (M6)
OL,4,Cand Scotch Corner set to begin this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"Investment in dualling the remaining
OL,8,Fsingle carriageway sections between
OL,9,Fthe M6 and A1(M) will significantly
OL,10,Fimprove journey times and safety, as
OL,11,Fwell as providing additional
OL,12,Fresilience to trans-Pennine journeys
OL,13,Fwhich currently rely on the M62
OL,14,Fcorridor."
OL,16,FLocal residents have long called for
OL,17,Fthe A66 to be turned into a dual
OL,18,Fcarriageway, to improve connectivity
OL,19,Fand safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1774563066
OL,3,CDualling of A66 between Penrith (M6)
OL,4,Cand Scotch Corner set to begin this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FOne local told ITV Border: "Basically
OL,8,Fget on with it. I mean, the number of
OL,9,Faccidents and deaths that only stretch
OL,11,Fthere's been, there has been a lot of
OL,12,Fterrible accidents and shocking,
OL,13,Fshocking roads."
OL,15,FAnother said: "I just think for safety
OL,16,Freasons, the whole A66 would be better
OL,17,Fif it was dual carriageway."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
