OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1774563066
OL,3,CDualling of A66 between Penrith (M6)
OL,4,Cand Scotch Corner set to begin this
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FReacting to the announcement, MP for
OL,8,FWestmorland and Lonsdale Tim Farron
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's encouraging that they are
OL,10,Frestating their commitment to this,
OL,11,Fbut frustrating that the timescale is
OL,12,Fso vague.
OL,14,F"We'd add that while news that the A66
OL,15,Fwork will soon be starting is
OL,16,Fencouraging, and a result of our hard
OL,17,Fwon local campaign, it makes it even
OL,18,Fmore important that (M6) Junction 38
OL,19,Fis kept open because the disruption by
OL,20,Fboth happening at the same time is
OL,21,Fgoing to be off the scale."
